scripts.deploy-next: rm -rf docs && next build && touch out/.nojekyll && git add out/ && git commit -m "Deploy" && git subtree push --prefix out origin gh-pages
scripts.deploy-no-commit: rm -rf docs && next build && touch out/.nojekyll && mv out docs && git add docs/
scripts.deploy: rm -rf docs && next build && touch out/.nojekyll && mv out docs && git add docs/ && git commit -m "Deploy" && git checkout gh-pages && git push
